      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '6-22-26 Gavin Notes


    Add controllers with any button, then click
    which scene you want to load into. If you want your monster to be a flying monster,
    click on the appropriate button.


    What''s New:


    - The Beastdome is
    now fully playable! Jam packed with 5 stage events which cycle over time. While
    I imagine them being random, I have made them go in order for easier testing.
    These events include new hazard types like electric ropes and anti air launchers


    -
    Beastdome Stadium Camera follows players in the midst of battle!


    - Elevators
    have (hopefully) been fixed'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
